## Animation Guidelines

### Duration Standards

```css
/* Quick interactions (hover, focus) */
duration: 200ms

/* Standard animations (fade, slide) */
duration: 300-500ms

/* Page transitions */
duration: 800ms

/* Complex animations (background effects) */
duration: 2-5s (loop)
```

### Easing Functions

```css
/* Ease Out (default) - natural deceleration */
cubic-bezier(0.0, 0.0, 0.2, 1)

/* Ease In Out - smooth both ends */
cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.2, 1)

/* Spring - bouncy effect */
cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55)
```

### Animation Performance

- ✅ **Animate**: transform, opacity, filter
- ❌ **Avoid**: width, height, top, left, margin
- Use `will-change` for complex animations
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`

