## Design Principles Summary

1. **Consistency**: Use design tokens from this system
2. **Hierarchy**: Clear visual hierarchy with size, weight, color
3. **Spacing**: Never overlap, always maintain minimum spacing
4. **Performance**: GPU-accelerated animations only
5. **Accessibility**: WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
6. **Responsiveness**: Mobile-first, test all breakpoints
7. **Theming**: Support both light and dark modes
8. **Motion**: Meaningful animations, respect reduced motion

